title: Capital Organic
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Indian, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic and health food restaurant at the cross roads that lead to Patnem beach. Offers both western as well as some Indian food: stuffed vegetable, stir frys, curries, salads, in-house-made bread, juices, and more.
